node.text: Had the best time launching my very own “LIANE” Ponytail with one of my fave brands @insertnamehere 💕 Also being able to work with amazing talented people, and see my vision come to life is so unreal! I love and enjoy every second of it! And I’m able to do all this because of YOU! My supporters and motivators! I appreciate and love you all so much! 🥺You keep me going! 👏🏽😘 Stay tuned for more fun projects like this! Can’t wait to share what I have planned for 2021 😏🎉

node.title: One of my highlights of this year! 💫
